# Architecture Constraints

## Dual-Path Migration

This project is migrating from direct Supabase calls to a C# API gateway. ALL data access MUST support both paths via feature flag until migration completes.

**Pattern**:

```typescript
import { shouldUseCSharpApi } from '@/config/environment';

if (shouldUseCSharpApi()) {
  // C# API path
} else {
  // Legacy Supabase path
}
```

## Layer Separation

Application layer must NEVER reference Infrastructure:

- DTOs → `Retroscope.Application/`
- Implementations → `Retroscope.Infrastructure/`

## Test-Driven Development

Write failing tests BEFORE implementation. No exceptions.
